| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2099 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9dd6c5dd-4f56-5457-8a7d-8a1614b43d71"
